Detailed Description

PbEntryShowAction analyzes if the input string has the meaning of showing a telephonebook entry with the syntax "sim-recno#" e.g. "23#" will show the record 23 of the ADN phonebook. Execute has to be overwritten to implement the showing of this phonebook entry.
